600000678697	2022-03-25	202206	2022-06-03	Scheduled Reactive Service	[  "25.03.2022 08:11:40   I. Siemens Healthineers (MEDINVL) Phone 1522/2..*** Issue reported ***Mon_C25 : The CAN24 module of MR174769 in DE is not reporting anymore, last was 2022-03-21 02:03:00 on Tue Mar 22 14:22:52 2022Original message:Node:          MR10838610-174769Message group:Application:   MED_MR_HeMonObject:        EMEASeverity:      MajorText:          Mon_C25 : The CAN24 module of MR174769 in DEis not reporting anymore, last was 2022-03-21 02:03:00Time first received: 2022/03/22 14:22:55Time last received: 2022/03/22 15:22:55No. of duplicates since time first received: 0Event Instructions:Mon_C25:Explanation:\\tThe CAN24 didn't send information from the MSUP for over25hours.\\tConsequence:\\t1. No Magnet specific information if the MR system is switched off\\t2. No information about Helium loss.\\t3. No information if helium compressor switched off.\\t3. No Information in case of a Quench\\t4. Magnet will warm up in case of cooling problems.\\tAction:\\t\\tPerfom the actions in the following order:\\t1. Check the ftp-connection between CAN and the SRS server:\\t1.1 Log in to CAN24 via WEB_IF\\t1.2 Start the  &quot;Test Message Transfer&quot; and checkthe &quot;T DATA&quot; file on the RDIAG server.\\t1.3 Check the CAN Box Configuration on the Administration Portal.\\t2. Check the supply voltage of CAN24, router and customer network.\\t3. Check the correct ftp-transfer configuration of the customer network.\\t4. Contact the SRS Help Desk.na*** Action taken ***na25.03.2022 08:11:50   I. Siemens Healthineers (MEDINVL) Phone 1522/2..0001/PROA2022/03/25 09:11:42 Florian Koerner  Ticket raised in PEAK25.03.2022 08:12:04   I. Siemens Healthineers (MEDINVL) Phone 1522/2..0003/RESP2022/03/25 09:11:57 Florian Koerner  The escalated Call has generated the following Ticket number: PEAK163847925.03.2022 08:14:51   Florian Koerner ( )  @Disp:Proaktive MeldungNicht mit dem Kunden gesprochen.Bitte zei