600002077567	2023-11-07	202311	2023-11-10	Scheduled Reactive Service	[  "07.11.2023 04:37:00   I. Siemens Healthineers (MEDINVL) Phone 1522/2..Mon_SEC - Physikalisch-Technische, Berlin (DE) The cleaningof the SEP secondary water strainer has to be planned in the next three months. on Tue Nov 07 04:57:00 2023Original message:Node:          MR11647158-213007Message group:Application:   MED_MR_HeMonObject:        EMEASeverity:      WarningText:          Mon_SEC : Physikalisch-Technische, Berlin (DE) The cleaning of the SEP secondary water strainer has to be planned in the next three months.Time first received: 2023/11/07 04:57:03Time last received: 2023/11/07 05:57:03No. of duplicates since time first received: 0Event Instructions:Explanation:\\tThe Magnet&amp;Cooling Pump Revolution value shows a high chance of a dirty secondary water strainer.\\tConsequence:\\t1. Secondary water temperature will increase.\\t2. Scanning will be stopped.\\t3. Helium compressor will be stopped.\\t4. Magnet will lose Helium.Action:\\t1. Check and clean the secondary water strainer.\\t2. Check for closed ball valve.\\t3. Check water hoses for bends and kinks.\\t4. Check water pressure.\\t5. Refill water if necessary.\\t6. Re-charge the auto refill device: Pressure should be between 4 - 6 bar.\\t7. Check the primary water circuit.\\t8. Check and clean the primary water strainer.Tools required:\\tAdjustable spanner (55mm)\\tNeedle nose pliers\\tWater pump for water filling\\tCloth to absorb waterRequired time: 60 min07.11.2023 04:37:08   I. Siemens Healthineers (MEDINVL) Phone 1522/2..0001/PROA2023/11/07 04:37:06 PK GSMS Integration User  PhoneProactive Notification posted.07.11.2023 06:04:01   Florian Koerner ( )  @Disp:Proaktive MeldungNicht mit dem Kunden gesprochen.Bei der n?chsten Wartung/Gelegenheit, oder sp?testens in 3 Monatensollen bitte auch die Wasserfilter gereinigt werden.AZ: !#DUR:60#!Der Kunde kann dabei nicht arbeiten.* 07.11.2023 06:04:20   Florian Koerner ( )  *** Action T