600002872004	2024-05-07	202405	2024-05-08	Repair due to Partially Down	[   "07.05.2024 04:29:17   Joanne Allen ( )",   "*** Issue Reported ***",   "POWER Outage whole site",   "*** Action Taken ***",   "FCC Raised to Mark Cutajar after phone message passed on",   "",   "07.05.2024 08:49:05   Mark Cutajar ( )",   "<<<<<<<<< REPORTTEXT >>>>>>>>>> by Mark CUTAJAR",   "*** Action Taken ***:Cutajar Mark",   "The EPO main contactor had blown causing the sites street fuses to blow",   "resulting in now",   "power to the site. Customer has bypassed the EPO breaker until one has",   "been sourced and",   "they have been made away that if the EPO button is pressed, the mains",   "power will still be",   "on and that power needed to be switched off from the equipment room",   "directly.",   "When power was restored to the site, the system would not turn on. The",   "UPS was showing an",   "alarm. Customer (Andrew) stated that none of the EPO switches had been",   "activated. The UPS",   "was bypassed with the bypass plug on top of the equipment cabinet. With",   "the ups bypassed,",   "the system booted up into the Home Screen. Logged into the system and",   "found magnet",   "pressure at 16.3 PSI due to the cold head being off. All other magnet",   "cooling parameters",   "are ok. During the online checks, found the ERDU test had failed and",   "this will need to be",   "looked at during the next visit.",   "<<<<<<<<< REPORT-CODES >>>>>>>>>",   "800 - Homework",   "07.05.2024 08:49:09   Mark Cutajar ( )",   "***** Internal note – Info to dispatcher *****",   "Please order 1 3KVA GXT5 USV UPS part number 11647157. Please also ask",   "local engineer timing required as they may want t",   "o team up the visit when the local electrician replaces the faulty EPO",   "contactor. The system is currently running with t",   "he EPO contactor bypassed as well as the UPS. Thanks",   "08.05.2024 00:08:51   Donald Makhura ( )",   "<<<<<<<<< REPORTTEXT >>>>>>>>>> by Donald MAKHURA",   "***