600000322217	2020-11-04	202011	2020-11-05	Repair due to Partially Down	[  "04.11.2020 12:00:30   I. Siemens Healthineers (MEDINVL) Phone 1522/2..Mon_CAN : 202008 (CH) The CAN24 module is not reporting anymore on Wed Nov 04 12:59:37 2020Original message:Node:          MR11410481-202008Message group:Application:   MED_MR_HeMonObject:        EMEASeverity:      WarningText:          Mon_CAN : 202008 (CH) The CAN24 module is not reporting anymoreTime first received: 2020/11/04 12:59:40Time last received: 2020/11/04 13:59:40No. of duplicates since time first received: 0Event Instructions:Explanation: The CAN24 module is not reporting any more. This module is supposed to monitor the magnet while the MR system is off.Probably, the firmware is hung up.Consequence:\\tWithout connection to the CAN24, you will not be informed if environmental parameters (e.g. water temperature) or Magnet parameters are exceeding their limits.\\tAfter hour Quenches cannot be reported as well.\\tAction:\\tIf the CAN24 module has never been connected, please do asdescribed in the Installation Guide.\\tIf the CAN24 module was working before, trouble shoot onsite and/or contact the SRS Helpdesk for analysis of Router and Firewall.\\t\\tPlease press the Reset button on the CAN24 module to restart it.\\tAlternatively, use F41 to reset the CAN module while the MR system is switched off. Switch the breaker off, wait for 10 seconds and switch back on again.\\t\\tCheck at  https://mrqprod.med.siemens.com/mrquality/mr/format/Index1.htm under &quot;RDIAG Coverage&quot; -&gt; &quot;CAN24&quot; if other sites in your country also are missing the CAN24 connectivity.04.11.2020 12:00:35   I. Siemens Healthineers (MEDINVL) Phone 1522/2..0001/PROA2020/11/04 12:00:34 PK GSMS Integration User  PhoneProactive Notification posted.04.11.2020 15:30:05   Niels Hennet ( )  ***#Resolution Provided#***disp05.11.2020 16:02:20   Martin Sarbach ( )  <<<<<<<<< REPORTTEXT >>>>>>>>>> by Martin SARBACH*** Resolution ***:Sarbach MartinMon_CAN : 202008 (CH) The CAN24 module is not reporting anymore onWed Nov 04 12:59:37 2020Remote überprüft, Last send date: Nov. 05 2020Call closed<<<<<<<<< REPORT-CODES >>>>>>>>>"]	11410481	202008	VIDA	MAGNETOM VIDA FIT	The CAN24 module stopped reporting, affecting magnet and environmental monitoring during system downtime	Remote check performed to verify the last send date of the CAN24 module	No corrective action was taken	CAN24 Module Reporting Failures	Magnet	202011	CH	Switzerland	2020-11-05	NULL	NULL	110
