600000324236	2020-11-08	202011	2020-11-08	Repair due to Partially Down	[  "08.11.2020 16:15:49   I. Siemens Healthineers (MEDINVL) Phone 1522/2..Mon_C25 : The CAN24 module of MR176055 in DE is not reporting anymore, last was 2020-11-07 02:28:00 on Sun Nov 08 17:14:51 2020Original message:Node:          MR11060815-176055Message group:Application:   MED_MR_HeMonObject:        EMEASeverity:      MajorText:          Mon_C25 : The CAN24 module of MR176055 in DEis not reporting anymore, last was 2020-11-07 02:28:00Time first received: 2020/11/08 17:14:53Time last received: 2020/11/08 18:14:53No. of duplicates since time first received: 0Event Instructions:Mon_C25:Explanation:\\tThe CAN24 didn't send information from the MSUP for over25hours.\\tConsequence:\\t1. No Magnet specific information if the MR system is switched off\\t2. No information about Helium loss.\\t3. No information if helium compressor switched off.\\t3. No Information in case of a Quench\\t4. Magnet will warm up in case of cooling problems.\\tAction:\\t\\tPerfom the actions in the following order:\\t1. Check the ftp-connection between CAN and the SRS server:\\t1.1 Log in to CAN24 via WEB_IF\\t1.2 Start the  &quot;Test Message Transfer&quot; and checkthe &quot;T DATA&quot; file on the RDIAG server.\\t1.3 Check the CAN Box Configuration on the Administration Portal.\\t2. Check the supply voltage of CAN24, router and customer network.\\t3. Check the correct ftp-transfer configuration of the customer network.\\t4. Contact the SRS Help Desk.08.11.2020 16:15:53   I. Siemens Healthineers (MEDINVL) Phone 1522/2..0001/PROA2020/11/08 04:15:52 PK GSMS Integration User  PhoneProactive Notification posted.08.11.2020 16:15:54   I. Siemens Healthineers (MEDINVL) Phone 1522/2..0002/WIPR2020/11/08 04:15:52 PK GSMS Integration User  PhoneProactive Notification posted.09.11.2020 06:33:58   I. Siemens Healthineers (MEDINVL) Phone 1522/2..0003/RESP2020/11/09 07:33:51 KOERNER FLORIAN 21026805 Phone +49 (9131) 9889-4746KOERNER