600002080039	2023-11-07	202311	2023-11-08	Repair due to Partially Down	[  "07.11.2023 16:45:22   I. Siemens Healthineers (MEDINVL) Phone 1522/2..MRI_C24_RampUpfail - * switch heater fault on Tue Nov 07 16:18:24 2023Original message:Node:          MR11408425-206025Message group:Application:   MED_MR_CANObject:        EMEASeverity:      WarningText:          MRI_C24_810 : * switch heater faultTime first received: 2023/11/07 16:18:27Time last received: 2023/11/07 17:18:27No. of duplicates since time first received: 0Event Instructions:Explanation:Scanning is not possibleThe following reasons can cause this problem:1.) Operational failure of the switch heater was detected.2.) The UPS signals indicate it is in an alarm condition.3.) MPS Cable test current limit exceeded (MPS error 7)4.) Ramp up attempt failed because RDL Rundownload test sequence was unsuccessful.5.) MPS operation inhibited due to RDL temperature is out of range.Action:Remotely1.) Check Heater, RundownLoad and MiniUPS values in Magnet&amp;Cooling/Magnet Status2.) Check all cooling values in Magnet&amp;Cooling/Cooling Status3.) Download the related logfiles in Magnet&amp;Cooling/Magnet Status for further investigation.4.) Download the MSCU logs (RDL test, MPS Self Test, RampUp) in Repair/Magnet Ramping for further investigation.Onsite1.) Check the cabling at the MSCU and give it a reset.2.) Check the function and the LEDs status of the MiniUPS devices (Powersupply and controller) in the EPC.3.) Check the temperature sensor on top of the run down load in the magnet room.4.) Re-Run the MPS selftest in Magnet&amp;Cooling/MagnetRampSetupFurther actions to be determined with RSC and/or Magnet HSC.07.11.2023 16:45:30   I. Siemens Healthineers (MEDINVL) Phone 1522/2..0001/PROA2023/11/07 04:45:28 PK GSMS Integration User  PhoneProactive Notification posted.08.11.2023 17:49:46   Martin Haring ( )<<<<<<<<< REPORTTEXT >>>>>>>>>> by Martin HARING*** Resolution ***:Haring MartinC1. Vypadok napajacieho napatia - vymena privodneho kablaC2. Problem je docasny (doba nevyhnutna na vymenu privodu)C3. Objasnenie prevedene telefonickyC4. Pri servisnom vykone neboli prená?ané ?iadne pacientske údajeC5. Nebola ohrozená bezpecnost pacientaC6. Porucha sa po oprave neprejavila, zariadenie je funkcne a pripravenena prevadzku-kontrola systemu po pripojeni privodu-technici opacne nafazovali privod-upozornenie k naprave-opatovna kontrola systemu (ok)<<<<<<<<< REPORT-CODES >>>>>>>>>08.11.2023 17:49:57   I. Siemens Healthineers (MEDINVL) Phone 1522/2..0011/HQCO2023/11/08 05:49:53 PK SAP Country Integration User  Phone*** Resolution **** 08.11.2023 17:49:46   Martin Haring ( )CRM FOR TASK 0003 2023-11-08 18:49:46 CSE Haring MartinShort text: FOR TASK 0003Long text:*** Resolution ***:Haring MartinC1. Vypadok napajacieho napatia - vymena privodneho kablaC2. Problem je docasny (doba nevyhnutna na vymenu privodu)C3. Objasnenie prevedene telefonickyC4. Pri servisnom vykone neboli prená?ané ?iadne pacientskeúdajeC5. Nebola ohrozená bezpecnost pacientaC6. Porucha sa po oprave neprejavila, zariadenie je funkcnea pripravenena prevadzku-kontrola systemu po pripojeni privodu-technici opacne nafazovali privod-upozornenie k naprave-opatovna kontrola systemu (ok)RSC final safety assessment result NNN"]	11408425	206025	FREE.MAX	MAGNETOM FREE.MAX	Switch heater fault caused by power supply failure and misphased cable connection	Replaced the power supply cable Corrected the cable phasing Performed system checks to ensure functionality	Replaced the power supply cable Corrected the cable phasing	Switch and Heater Faults	Power Supply	202311	SK	Slovakia	2023-11-09	N	VA50A-SP01	110
