600000028216	2019-01-05	201901	2019-01-10	Repair due to Partially Down	[  "05.01.2019 04:07:19   I. Siemens Healthineers (MEDINVL) Phone 1522/2..Mon_LOSS - This 4K magnet (DE) shows Helium Loss. https://mrqprod.med.siemens.com/mrquality/work/default.aspx?Nummer=175736&Sel=8 on Sat Jan 05 05:05:19 2019Original message:Node:          MR11060815-175736Message group:Application:   MED_MR_HeMonObject:        EMEASeverity:      MajorText:          Mon_LOSS : This 4K magnet (DE) shows Helium Loss. https://mrqprod.med.siemens.com/mrquality/work/default.aspx?Nummer=175736&Sel=8Time first received: 2019/01/05 05:07:01Time last received: 2019/01/05 06:07:01No. of duplicates since time first received: 0Event Instructions:The 4K magnet shows Helium loss.Explanation:The magnet shows Helium boil off, more than 0.9% over one week.Consequence:1. Helium level will decrease to alarm level.2. Scanning will be stopped.Action:1. Check the magnet pressure (MP):If MP = 15.3 psi ==> check venting assembly for leakage,check that the bypass valve is closed.Check the 16 psi valve:If MP > 15.3 psi and < 15.9 psi ==> 16 psi valve is leaky ==> replace the 16 psi valve assembly.If MP > 16.0 psi ==> continue with step 2.2. Check the cooling performance of the cold head via MR Quality page: pressure heater average power, MP.3. Check the static gas pressure of the compressor.4. Check that the pressure heater is off.5. Search/repair Helium leakage.6. Check that the bypass valves are closed.7. Replace the cold head.----------------------------------------------------------------Historic Activities:--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------07.01.2019 10:54:12   Thorsten Lutz ( )  @Disp:Proaktive MeldungNicht mit dem Kunden gesprochen.Bitte  Einsatz vor Ort planen um den Kompressordruck zu überprüfen undggf. nach TSG anpassen.He Gas 5.0 wird ben?tigt!Einsatz sollte innerhalb der n?chsten 2 Tage stattfinden.Zeitbedarf ca. 0,5h. Kunde kann nebenher arbeiten.* 07.01.2019 10:55:09   Thorsten Lutz ( )  *** Action Taken ***: * 07.01.2019 10:55:00   Thorsten Lutz ( )----------------------------------------12.01.2019 10:05:18   Dirk Real ( )<<<<<<<<< REPORTTEXT >>>>>>>>>> by Dirk REAL*** Resolution ***:Real DirkKein Heliumverlust. Anlage hat nur in den EcoMode gewechselt.<<<<<<<<< REPORT-CODES >>>>>>>>>"]	11060815	175736	VIDA	MAGNETOM VIDA	System switched to EcoMode, initially mistaken for helium loss	Planned on-site visit to check compressor pressure Determined no helium loss occurred	Confirmed system was operating in EcoMode; no further action required	Helium Level and Loss	Magnet	201901	DE	Germany	2019-07-05	N	VA20A-SP07	110
