gradient coil is concerned, please contact HSC first.8.) If all repairs are done successfully or if no indications for the malfunctionscan be found:- Reset the VLM device.- Create Savelog and inform HSC for further investigation. TheSavelog contains 2 VLM-specific files (VLMK2309Statistics.utr andVLMK2309Statistics1.utr)Info:The VLM device checks for smoke or high pollution at:- the gradient connections (at gradient coil)- the gradient filters- the electronic cabinets- the Body Coil (e.g. broken capacitors or pin diodes)----------------------------------------------------------------Historic Activities:--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------23.01.2019 14:47:08   Thorsten Lutz ( )  Die Anlage wird derzeit noch inbetrieb genommen.----------------------------------------23.01.2019 14:47:48   Thorsten Lutz ( )  *** Resolution ***: * 23.01.2019 14:47:55   Thorsten Lutz ( ) P."]	11060815	175743	VIDA	MAGNETOM VIDA	Smoke concentration exceeded fire-1 threshold, triggering system shutdown	No troubleshooting steps were recorded	No corrective action was taken	Environmental Interference	Environment	201901	DE	Germany	2019-01-23	N	VA20A-SP06	110
