600002083309	2023-11-09	202311	2023-11-09	Repair due to Partially Down	[  "09.11.2023 07:10:59   I. Siemens Healthineers (MEDINVL) Phone 1522/2..*** Issue reported ***Mon_LOSS - This 4K magnet (FR) shows Helium Loss on Thu Nov09 01:51:47 2023Original message:Node:          MR10838610-174826Message group:Application:   MED_MR_HeMonObject:        EMEASeverity:      MajorText:          Mon_LOSS : This 4K magnet (FR) shows Helium LossTime first received: 2023/11/09 01:51:49Time last received: 2023/11/09 02:51:49No. of duplicates since time first received: 0Event Instructions:The 4K magnet shows Helium loss.Explanation:\\tThe magnet shows Helium boil off, more than 0.9% over one week.Consequence:1. Helium level will decrease to alarm level.2. Scanning will be stopped.Action:\\t1. Check the magnet pressure (MP):    If MP = 15.3 psi ==&gt; check venting assembly for leakage,                                      check that the bypassvalve is closed.                                      Check the 16 psi valve:    If MP &gt; 15.3 psi and &lt; 15.9 psi ==&gt; 16 psi valve is leaky ==&gt; replace the 16 psi valve assembly.    If MP &gt; 16.0 psi ==&gt; continue with step 2.2. Check the cooling performance of the cold head via MR Quality page: pressure heater average power, MP.3. Check the static gas pressure of the compressor.4. Check that the pressure heater is off.5. Search/repair Helium leakage.6. Check that the bypass valves are closed.7. Replace the cold head.na*** Action taken ***na09.11.2023 07:11:08   I. Siemens Healthineers (MEDINVL) Phone 1522/2..0001/PROA2023/11/09 08:11:02 Florian Koerner  Ticket raised in PEAK09.11.2023 07:11:31   I. Siemens Healthineers (MEDINVL) Phone 1522/2..0003/RESP2023/11/09 08:11:27 Florian Koerner  The escalated Call has generated the following Ticket number: PEAK407611009.11.2023 12:10:16   Anthony Gautier ( )reprise shim lundi 06/11 sur autre avissuivre niveau He ces prochains jours21.11.2023 15:34:54   Anthony Gautier ( )niveau helium stable depuis le 07/1121.11.2023 15:35:57   Anthony Gautier ( )*** Resolution ***: * 21.11.2023 15:36:09   Anthony Gautier ( )09.11.2023 07:10:59   I. Siemens Healthineers (MEDINVL) Phone 1522/2..*** Issue reported ***Mon_LOSS - This 4K magnet (FR) shows Helium Loss on Thu Nov09 01:51:47 2023/09.11.2023 12:10:16   Anthony Gautier ( )reprise shim lundi 06/11 sur autre avissuivre niveau He ces prochains jours21.11.2023 15:34:54   Anthony Gautier ( )niveau helium stable depuis le 07/1121.11.2023 15:37:41   I. Siemens Healthineers (MEDINVL) Phone 1522/2..0005/HQCO2023/11/21 03:37:31 PK SAP Country Integration User  Phone*** Resolution **** 21.11.2023 15:37:20   Anthony Gautier ( )CRM FOR TASK 0002 2023-11-21 16:36:10 CSE Gautier AnthonyShort text: FOR TASK 0002Long text:*** Resolution ***: * 21.11.2023 15:36:09   Anthony Gautier ( )09.11.2023 07:10:59   I. Siemens Healthineers (MEDINVL) Phone 1522/2..*** Issue reported ***Mon_LOSS - This 4K magnet (FR) shows Helium Loss on Thu Nov09 01:51:47 2023/09.11.2023 12:10:16   Anthony Gautier ( )reprise shim lundi 06/11 sur autre avissuivre niveau He ces prochains jours21.11.2023 15:34:54   Anthony Gautier ( )niveau helium stable depuis le 07/11RSC final safety assessment result NNN"]	10838610	174826	AMIRA	MAGNETOM AMIRA	Helium loss exceeding 0.9% over one week in the 4K magnet system	Monitored helium levels over several days Performed shim adjustment on November 6	Helium levels stabilized as of November 7, resolving the issue	Helium Level and Loss	Magnet	202311	FR	Germany	2023-11-22	N	VA50M-SP01	110
