600002087767	2023-11-11	202311	2023-11-11	Scheduled Reactive Service	[  "11.11.2023 04:02:21   I. Siemens Healthineers (MEDINVL) Phone 1522/2..Mon_CSS : *High number of compressor stops 8 on 1 days (MR1) on Sat Nov 11 04:44:11 2023Original message:Node:          MR10432915-46029Message group:Application:   MED_MR_HeMonObject:        Asia-PacificSeverity:      MajorText:          Mon_CSS : *High number of compressor stops 8on 1 days (MR1)Time first received: 2023/11/11 04:43:01Time last received: 2023/11/11 05:43:01No. of duplicates since time first received: 0Event Instructions:Explanation: Coldhead Compressor is cycling On &amp; Off.Consequence:1. Increased magnet pressure.2. Higher Shield Temp and increased Helium Boil-off.3. Premature failure of the Coldhead or the Compressor.Action:1. Verify if stops are caused by any power outage or chiller breakdown and make concerned persons aware of it.2. Check for any error on the compressor display3. Refer to system log to investigate compressor Stop-Starttiming.\\tFor Avanto/Espree/Verio systems download    C:\\\\MedCom\\\\log\\\\MSUPHistory.log file,\\tFor Aera/Skyra etc download  C:\\\\MedCom\\\\log\\\\MSUCompressorStartHistory.log and MSUCompressorStopHistory.log file.4. Investigate compressor water flow in day and night mode5. Investigate compressor water temperature in night mode6. If  Helium pressure drops below &quot;Atmospheric pressure +0.2-psig&quot;, the compressor is disabled to stop the He re-liquefaction process, thus preventing sub-atmospheric magnet pressure. No action necessary.Water Specification:Cooling water flow rate 6-9l/min. (1.6 to 2.4 gpm)Cooling water temp 5-25°C (41-77° F)Cooling water outlet temperature 45°C (113° F) maximum11.11.2023 04:02:31   I. Siemens Healthineers (MEDINVL) Phone 1522/2..0001/PROA2023/11/11 04:02:30 PK GSMS Integration User  PhoneProactive Notification posted.12.11.2023 20:26:18   Juergen Schneider ( )*** Action Taken ***S/A:  NNNLogged into the system and checked magnet and cooling status: magnetSite experienced issues with primary water supply / chiller to theChiller not under contract12.11.2023 20:26:38   Juergen Schneider ( )0003/HQUPS/A:  NNNLogged into the system and checked magnet and cooling status: magnetvalues normal, cooling ok; pump and cold head running.Site experienced issues with primary water supply / chiller to thesystem that stopped pump and compressor.  Water supply restored.Chiller not under contract12.11.2023 20:29:21   Juergen Schneider ( )*** Resolution ***: * 12.11.2023 20:29:51   Juergen Schneider ( /A:  NNNLogged into can24 and checked magnet and cooling status: magnet valuesnormal , cooling ok; pump and cold head running.Site experienced issues with primary water supply / chiller to thesystem that stopped pump and compressor.  Water supply restored.Chiller not under contract12.11.2023 20:31:04   I. Siemens Healthineers (MEDINVL) Phone 1522/2..0006/HQCO2023/11/12 08:31:00 PK SAP Country Integration User  Phone*** Resolution **** 12.11.2023 20:30:54   Juergen Schneider ( )CRM FOR TASK 0002 2023-11-13 06:29:52 CSE Schneider JuergenShort text: FOR TASK 0002Long text:*** Resolution ***: * 12.11.2023 20:29:51   Juergen Schneider ( /A:  NNNLogged into can24 and checked magnet and cooling status: magnet valuesnormal , cooling ok; pump and cold head running.Site experienced issues with primary water supply / chillerto thesystem that stopped pump and compressor.  Water supply restored.Chiller not under contractRSC final safety assessment result NNN"]	10432915	46029	SKYRA	MAGNETOM SKYRA 3T	Frequent compressor stops due to primary water supply/chiller issues	Logged into the system and checked magnet and cooling status Confirmed magnet values were normal Verified cooling system was operational Checked that the pump and cold head were running Restored the primary water supply	Restored the primary water supply Confirmed normal operation of magnet and cooling systems	Cooling System Failures	Environment	202311	AU	Australia	