600000340586	2020-12-07	202012	2020-12-07	Repair due to Partially Down	[  "07.12.2020 12:30:34   I. Siemens Healthineers (MEDINVL) Phone 1522/2..MRI_COO_32  Cooling System / COO: Return pressure in secondary water circuit is high.Please contact Siemens Service.COO_RETURNPRESSUREHIGHWARNING_STATUSSeverity: Warningon Mon Dec 07 13:30:09 2020Original message:Computer: \\tAWP175001Source:      \\tMRI_COO_SysLogServiceCategory: \\tNoneType:        \\tWarningEvent ID: \\t0Description:\\tMessage: Cooling System / COO: Return pressurein secondary water circuit is high.Please contact Siemens Service.ID: syngo.MR.MRI_COO_NlsMessageId.Resources.COOmsg.MRI_COO_W_32_COO_RETURNPRESSUREHIGHWARNING_STATUSSeverity: WarningInformation: : : : UserTimestamp: 2020-12-07T13:30:09.138+01:00Machine: AWP175001Process Name: C:\\\\Program Files\\\\Siemens\\\\Numaris\\\\bin\\\\ParcServicesHost.exeProcess Id: 17808AppDomain: DefaultDomainProcess Start Time: 2020-12-07T07:34:43.971+01:00Extended Properties: MsgCreateTime - 2020-12-07T13:30:09.133+01:00OriginalSeverity - WarningTime first received: 2020/12/07 13:30:09Time last received: 2020/12/07 14:30:09No. of duplicates since time first received: 0Event Instructions:Explanation:The return pressure in the secondary water circuit reached the warning level (1.3 bar).Consequences:1.) Water cooled components in the secondary water circuit could be damaged.2.) Further pressure increase might stop scanning.Action:1.) Check the filling pressure. The static filling pressure(with water pump switched off) is 1 to 1.2 bar.2.) If necessary drain water from the secondary circuit to reach the filling pressure of 1 to 1.2 bar.3.) Check the gas pressure of the expansion vessel (normal gas pressure 0.7 bar +/- 0.1 bar)4.) Check function of sensor (for details see Information),replace sensor if necessary.Info:Error initiated by pressure sensor B4 in electric diagram or 8 in flow diagram.Pressure to current conversion:-0.5 to 9 barcorresponds to4 to 20 mADetailed information about the primary water temperature and the mixer position is included in the message MRI_COO 64 (severity: Informational).07.12.2020 12:30:39   I. Siemens Healthineers (MEDINVL) Phone 1522/2..0001/PROA2020/12/07 12:30:38 PK GSMS Integration User  PhoneProactive Notification posted.07.12.2020 12:30:40   I. Siemens Healthineers (MEDINVL) Phone 1522/2..0002/WIPR2020/12/07 12:30:38 PK GSMS Integration User  PhoneProactive Notification posted.07.12.2020 13:10:07   I. Siemens Healthineers (MEDINVL) Phone 1522/2..0003/RESP2020/12/07 14:10:06 KOERNER FLORIAN 21026805  KOERNER FLORIAN 21026805 is the agent responsible for the corresponding ticket IM08257973 in HQ.07.12.2020 13:10:14   I. Siemens Healthineers (MEDINVL) Phone 1522/2..0004/RESP2020/12/07 14:10:12 KOERNER FLORIAN 21026805  Return Pressure 1.35 barpressure should decrease the next time by itself20.01.2021 17:18:46   I. Siemens Healthineers (MEDINVL) Phone 1522/2..0005/HQCO2021/01/20 18:18:40 NITSCHE CHRISTIAN 20003552 Phone +49 (9131) 9889-4121PROA - automatic closing"]	10838610	175001	AMIRA	MAGNETOM AMIRA	High return pressure in the secondary water circuit reaching 1.35 bar	No troubleshooting steps were recorded	Pressure decreased by itself during subsequent operation	Pressure-Related	Cooling	202012	DE	Germany	2021-01-20	NULL	NULL	110
