kage.4.) Check the correct pressure regulator setting of the auto-refill device if the low pressure warning was reported although the auto-refill device pressure is correct.Info:Auto-refill device is a feature at newer SEPs. The auto-refill device should keep the secondary water return pressure constant on 1.0 bar untill it is filled over 1.0 bar. The auto-refill device should be filled in the range of 4.0 bar to 6.0 bar.08.12.2020 06:53:31   I. Siemens Healthineers (MEDINVL) Phone 1522/2..0001/PROA2020/12/08 06:53:31 PK GSMS Integration User  PhoneProactive Notification posted.08.12.2020 07:27:21   Florian Koerner ( ) Phone 9131/9889 4746@Disp:Proaktive MeldungNicht mit dem Kunden gesprochen.RP bei 0,71bar. Hier sollte innerhalb ein, zwei Wochen Wasser gefülltwerden.AZ ca. 0,5hDer Kunde kann dabei weiter arbeiten.* 08.12.2020 07:27:36   Florian Koerner ( )  *** Action Taken ***: * 08.12.2020 07:27:27   Florian Koerner ( 4.12.2020 08:40:56   Markus Fuerderer ( )<<<<<<<<< REPORTTEXT >>>>>>>>>> by Markus FüRDERER*** Resolution ***:Fürderer MarkusWasserdruck im Sekund?r Wasserkreislauf erh?ht<<<<<<<<< REPORT-CODES >>>>>>>>>"]	11060815	175751	VIDA	MAGNETOM VIDA	Low return pressure in the secondary water circuit (0.7 bar) compared to supply pressure (4.01 bar)	Engineer increased the water pressure in the secondary water circuit	Increasing the water pressure resolved the issue	Pressure-Related	Cooling	202012	DE	Germany	2020-12-14	NULL	NULL	110
