list.Required tools: n.a.Required service parts: n.a.Required time: 10 min14.04.2022 08:02:55   I. Siemens Healthineers (MEDINVL) Phone 1522/2..0001/PROA2022/04/14 08:02:54 PK GSMS Integration User  PhoneProactive Notification posted.14.04.2022 08:46:02   Thomas Thuermer ( )  Wir wurden hier Proaktiv informiert das die Anlage eine kleine Wartungben?tigt:Bitte TV mit Kd.(innerhalb von 3 Monaten) CSE einplanen.AZ: !#DUR:60#!Siehe  Anleitungen von oben.* 14.04.2022 08:46:37   Thomas Thuermer ( )  *** Action Taken ***: * 14.04.2022 08:46:26   Thomas Thuermer ( 4.04.2022 08:47:58   I. Siemens Healthineers (MEDINVL) Phone 1522/2..0005/HQCO2022/04/14 08:47:48 PK SAP Country Integration User  Phone*** Resolution **** 14.04.2022 08:47:43   Thomas Thuermer ( )  CRM FOR TASK 0002 2022-04-14 10:46:28 CSE Thürmer ThomasShort text: FOR TASK 0002Long text:*** Action Taken ***: * 14.04.2022 08:46:26   Thomas Thuermer ( SC final safety assessment result NNN14.04.2022 08:55:29   I. Siemens Healthineers ( )Modified By: Martina.Kopp@SiemensP1, Modified At: 2022-04-14T08:54:56.4226.04.2022 05:12:55   I. Siemens Healthineers ( )Modified By: background@SiemensP1, Modified At: 2022-04-26T05:09:50.24222.11.2022 06:11:52   I. Siemens Healthineers ( )Modified By: background@SiemensP1, Modified At: 2022-11-22T06:11:09.43524.11.2022 13:05:11   Roy Gutgesell ( )<<<<<<<<< REPORTTEXT >>>>>>>>>> by Roy GUTGESELL*** Resolution ***:Gutgesell RoyWartung durchgeführt. Anlage betriebsbereit.<<<<<<<<< REPORT-CODES >>>>>>>>>"]	11060815	176107	VIDA	MAGNETOM VIDA	Regular maintenance required for gradient filter fans, air inlets, and TFT monitor adjustment	Checked and cleaned gradient filter fans Cleaned air inlets and outlets Adjusted the TFT monitor	Completed all scheduled maintenance tasks and confirmed system operational	Maintenance and Testing Requests	Customer request	202204	DE	Germany	2022-11-24	N	VA20A-SP06	110
