600000349458	2020-12-23	202012	2020-12-23	Repair due to Partially Down	[  "23.12.2020 07:08:20   I. Siemens Healthineers (MEDINVL) Phone 1522/2..Mon_RET 3?60m times - Kühlsystem / COO: Der Rücklaufdruck im Sekund?rwasserkreislauf ist niedrig. Verst?ndigen Sie den Siemens Service. Der Rücklaufdruck betr?gt 0.49. on Wed Dec 23 08:02:14 2020Original message:Node:Message group:Application:   MRI_COOObject:        T_025_000Severity:      NormalText:          (57) - Kühlsystem / COO: Der Rücklaufdruck im Sekund?rwasserkreislauf ist niedrig. Verst?ndigen Sie den Siemens Service. Der Rücklaufdruck betr?gt 0.49.Time first received: 2020/12/23 08:07:42Time last received: 2020/12/23 09:07:42No. of duplicates since time first received: 0Event Instructions:RSCPC Explanation:The secondary water circuit of the SEP/IFP/ACS/COO is losing water.Consequence:1. Insufficient water pressure.2. Water pump will stop soon.3. Scanning will be stopped.4. Helium compressor will be stopped.5. Magnet will lose Helium.Action:Systems without auto refill device:1. Refill water.2. Check if the ball valve of expansion vessel is open.3. Check for leakage.Systems with auto refill device:1. Refill the auto refill device: Pressure should be between 4 - 6bar.    Refer to TSG / Cooling / Filling the auto_refill device2. Monitor the return pressure via SeSo. Water circuit should be filled from the auto refill device.3. Return pressure should increase to about 1.0bar.4. Re-charge the auto refill device: Pressure should be between 4 - 6bar.5. If no re-charging from the auto refill device:    Check the pressure regulator setting of the auto refilldevice (default setting is 1.0 bar)Info:While start-up it is normal because of automatic bleeding of the system.23.12.2020 07:08:24   I. Siemens Healthineers (MEDINVL) Phone 1522/2..0001/PROA2020/12/23 07:08:23 PK GSMS Integration User  PhoneProactive Notification posted.23.12.2020 07:15:48   Florian Koerner ( )  @Disp:Proaktive MeldungNicht mit dem Kunden gesprochen.RP bei 0,49bar. Hier sollte sofort Wasser gefüllt werden.AZ ca. 0,5hDer Kunde kann dabei weiter arbeiten.* 23.12.2020 07:16:09   Florian Koerner ( )  *** Action Taken ***: * 23.12.2020 07:15:54   Florian Koerner ( 8.12.2020 07:41:48   Thilo Kurz ( )  <<<<<<<<< REPORTTEXT >>>>>>>>>> by Thilo KURZ*** Resolution ***:Kurz ThiloKühlwasser auf 1,2bar aufgedrückt.<<<<<<<<< REPORT-CODES >>>>>>>>>"]	10836777	74011	AMIRA	MAGNETOM AMIRA	Low return pressure in the secondary water circuit of the cooling system, risking system shutdown	Refilled the cooling water Increased the pressure to 1.2 bar	Refilled the cooling water and increased pressure to 1.2 bar	Pressure-Related	Cooling	202012	DE	Germany	2020-12-28	N	VE11N-SP03	110
