600000360035	2021-01-17	202101	2021-01-17	Repair due to Partially Down	[  "17.01.2021 04:55:06   I. Siemens Healthineers (MEDINVL) Phone 1522/2..Mon_CAN : Dipl.-Med. Birgit Lipke, Brandenburg (DE) The CAN24 module is not reporting anymore on Sun Jan 17 05:54:06 2021Original message:Node:          MR10838610-175014Message group:Application:   MED_MR_HeMonObject:        EMEASeverity:      WarningText:          Mon_CAN : Dipl.-Med. Birgit Lipke, Brandenburg (DE) The CAN24 module is not reporting anymoreTime first received: 2021/01/17 05:54:08Time last received: 2021/01/17 06:54:08No. of duplicates since time first received: 0Event Instructions:Explanation: The CAN24 module is not reporting any more. This module is supposed to monitor the magnet while the MR system is off.Probably, the firmware is hung up.Consequence:\\tWithout connection to the CAN24, you will not be informed if environmental parameters (e.g. water temperature) or Magnet parameters are exceeding their limits.\\tAfter hour Quenches cannot be reported as well.\\tAction:\\tIf the CAN24 module has never been connected, please do asdescribed in the Installation Guide.\\tIf the CAN24 module was working before, trouble shoot onsite and/or contact the SRS Helpdesk for analysis of Router and Firewall.\\t\\tPlease press the Reset button on the CAN24 module to restart it.\\tAlternatively, use F41 to reset the CAN module while the MR system is switched off. Switch the breaker off, wait for 10 seconds and switch back on again.\\t\\tCheck at  https://mrqprod.med.siemens.com/mrquality/mr/format/Index1.htm under &quot;RDIAG Coverage&quot; -&gt; &quot;CAN24&quot; if other sites in your country also are missing the CAN24 connectivity.17.01.2021 04:55:11   I. Siemens Healthineers (MEDINVL) Phone 1522/2..0001/PROA2021/01/17 04:55:10 PK GSMS Integration User  PhoneProactive Notification posted.10.06.2021 13:52:07   I. Siemens Healthineers (MEDINVL) Phone 1522/2..0003/RESP2021/06/10 01:52:03 Truc Ahn Julia Pham PhoneThe escalated Call has generated the following Ticket number: PEAK061939710.06.2021 13:52:19   I. Siemens Healthineers (MEDINVL) Phone 1522/2..0004/HQCO2021/06/10 01:52:15 Truc Ahn Julia Pham Phone*** Resolution ***automatic closerRSC final safety assessment result NNNIssue Type: HWTrend Code: Y020Component / Main Modules: CUSTOMER REQU Sub Component: OTHERSCause: NO DEFECTPROA Closure Code: No action"]	10838610	175014	AMIRA	MAGNETOM AMIRA	The CAN24 module stopped reporting, affecting magnet and environmental monitoring during system downtime	No troubleshooting steps were recorded	No corrective action was taken	CAN24 Module Reporting Failures	Magnet	202101	DE	Germany	2021-08-04	N	VA12M-SP04	110
