st.Required tools: n.a.Required service parts: n.a.Required time: 10 min11.05.2022 10:31:12   I. Siemens Healthineers (MEDINVL) Phone 1522/2..0001/PROA2022/05/11 10:31:10 PK GSMS Integration User  PhoneProactive Notification posted.11.05.2022 12:09:41   Martin Sarbach ( )  *** Action Taken ***CBM BUNDLING: CBM_GFF, CBM_AWP, CBM_TFT uauf n?chste Wartung.Bitte call an St.Grundlehner, 1.Juli, 12:00, 1 Std.* 11.05.2022 12:10:04   Martin Sarbach ( )  *** Action Taken ***: * 11.05.2022 12:09:54   Martin Sarbach ( 11.05.2022 12:11:14   I. Siemens Healthineers (MEDINVL) Phone 1522/2..0005/HQCO2022/05/11 12:11:10 PK SAP Country Integration User  Phone*** Resolution **** 11.05.2022 12:11:03   Martin Sarbach ( )  CRM FOR TASK 0002 2022-05-11 14:09:56 CSE Sarbach MartinShort text: FOR TASK 0002Long text:*** Action Taken ***: * 11.05.2022 12:09:54   Martin Sarbach ( RSC final safety assessment result NNN31.05.2022 10:01:04   Alexis Francisco Lemus ( )*** Resolution ***Noti wird nicht gebraucht, da gleiche Noti bereits existiert. / Storno!"]	11060815	175670	VIDA	MAGNETOM VIDA	Potential overheating or misadjustment risks in gradient filter fans and related components	Bundled CBM tasks for next maintenance Scheduled a call for further action	No corrective action was taken	Cooling and Temperature	Gradient	202205	CH	Switzerland	2022-05-31	N	VA50A-SP01	120
